         <div type="translation">
            <p> Hylas, a charioteer of blue cloth, lived for twenty-five years. He won seven [times]
               with a youthful two-wheeled chariot, eleven [times] with a four-wheeled chariot,
               [and] having been called back three, he won second place thirty-nine [times] and
               third place forty-one [times].</p>
         </div>
